📌 CodSoft Internship - Python Programming

Task: Calculator Application
Internship: CodSoft Python Programming Internship

📖 Project Description

This project is a GUI-based Simple Calculator developed using Python's built-in Tkinter library. It allows users to perform basic arithmetic operations through an interactive graphical interface.

The application accepts two numerical inputs and performs one of the following operations:

➕ Addition
➖ Subtraction
✖️ Multiplication
➗ Division

The calculator also includes input validation, error handling, and utility features such as clearing inputs and exiting the application.

✨ Features
User-friendly graphical interface built with Tkinter.
Supports four basic arithmetic operations.
Validates empty input fields.
Handles invalid numeric input gracefully.
Prevents division by zero.
Automatically removes unnecessary decimal places for whole number results.
Clear button to reset all fields.
Exit button to close the application.
